      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2023-03-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2023-05-11T17:58:36Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Fortune for Fraud Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a Member of the House of Representatives from receiving compensation for a biography, a media appearance, or other creative work if the Member is convicted of specified felony offenses (e.g., bribing public officials or defrauding the government) or offenses related to violations of campaign finance laws. A Member who violates the prohibition shall be subject to a civil penalty of up to $10 million for each violation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
